  "title": "Lead Plumber",
  "description": "<p>We are plumbing service provider  looking for a skilled plumber in Singapore. Responsibilities include installing new plumbing systems, maintaining and repairing existing fixtures, and ensuring compliance with local codes. The ideal candidate should be adept at diagnostics, customer communication, and record-keeping. Join a dynamic team dedicated to delivering quality service and maintaining safety standards in plumbing.</p><h3>Responsibilities</h3><ul><li>Setting up new plumbing systems in new constructions or renovations.</li><li>Fixing leaks and clearing blockages.</li><li>Identifying plumbing issues and diagnosing problems with lines.</li></ul>",
